@startuml
[*] --> ReceiveRequest
ReceiveRequest --> IdentifyUser : identify user who made request
IdentifyUser --> GatherVideos : gather videos based on user's profile or preferences, trending videos from user’s area, videos with similar tags, videos from similar genres, and promoted videos
GatherVideos --> AddDetails : add additional details such as thumbnails and view counts to the suggested videos
AddDetails --> SendVideos : send the suggested videos to the user
SendVideos --> [*]
@enduml
